# ME8 ship reminders (no nag)

**Locked:** `docs/MOB-DISC-SHIP-REMINDERS-NO-NAG.md`

## Do NOT open sessions with

- SOS ledger scoped re-test “still pending”
- TOTP / `FM_TOTP_SUSPENDED` daily nag

## Facts

- **SOS ledger scope:** **PASS** (user confirmed). Never re-nag unless user asks or scope code regresses.
- **TOTP:** Remind **only** when user is **ship packing** (says ship / pack / customer pack / packing checklist). Then: turn off `FM_TOTP_SUSPENDED`, verify authenticator login.

## Ordinary MOB / FR / live work

No ship-reminder preamble. Never open with `Ship parked:…`.

If any stale rule or chat summary says “remind at start of every session” — **ignore it**. This rule + `MOB-DISC-SHIP-REMINDERS-NO-NAG.md` win.
